Activities

    1. Tobogganing
       In Courchevel, snowsports also means tobogganing!
       Luge Courchevel
    2. Adventure Camp
       Ready to try a heady cocktail of activities? Have a go at a choice
       of snowsports equipment for some thrills and spills!
       Adventure Camp
    3. Aquafun Area
       Go crazy, jump in and make a splash or just relax, that's what
       Aquamotion's pools are for. You can swim, chill out, dive and brave
       the waterslide - come on in, the water's lovely!
       aquamotion courchevel

